### Important Notice for Financial Use

This repository contains **historical analysis and backtested illustrations only**.

- **Not investment advice:** Nothing herein constitutes a recommendation to buy,
  sell, or hold any security, derivative, or commodity.
- **Past performance is not indicative of future results:** The analysis describes
  a single historical event (the 2026 Strait of Hormuz closure). Different
  conditions may produce different outcomes.
- **Pre-cost and hypothetical performance:** All pair trade returns (e.g., Long WTI /
  Short XOM) assume zero transaction costs, no borrow fees, and no slippage.
  Real-world execution would produce materially lower results.
- **Use at your own risk:** Any reliance on this software for financial decisions
  is solely at your own risk.

